==發行==
《厲陰宅2》原定於2015年10月23日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/warner-bros-scheduling-spree-continues-with-the-conjuring-2-mean-moms-2-others/|title=Warner Bros Scheduling Spree Continues With 'The Conjuring 2', 'Mean Moms', 2 Others|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=February 26, 2014|date=February 25, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619171103/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/warner-bros-scheduling-spree-continues-with-the-conjuring-2-mean-moms-2-others/|archive-date=2014-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年10月，華納兄弟將上映日改至2016年的一個未知日期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/2014/film/news/the-conjuring-sequel-pushed-back-to-2016-1201334951/|title='The Conjuring' Sequel Pushed Back to 2016|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=October 20, 2014|accessdate=October 21, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423224006/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-conjuring-sequel-pushed-back-to-2016-1201334951/|archive-date=2016-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年11月11日，宣布電影定於2016年6月10日上映，就如同前集一樣是在暑期推出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/2014/film/news/the-conjuring-2-release-date-1201353900/|title='The Conjuring 2' Set for June 10, 2016|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=November 11, 2014|accessdate=November 12, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423205320/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/the-conjuring-2-release-date-1201353900/|archive-date=2016-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《厲陰宅2》獲得正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據161篇專業影評獲得的新鮮度80%，平均得分6.56／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_conjuring_2/|title=The Conjuring 2 (2016)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=June 2, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531102645/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_conjuring_2/|archive-date=2016-05-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分64，整體評價以正面居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-conjuring-2|title=The Conjuring 2 reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|access-date=June 9, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603011404/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-conjuring-2|archive-date=2016-06-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。普遍認為儘管《厲陰宅2》不像前集如此恐怖，但仍維持著一貫順暢的敘事風格和質感，而其娛樂性則更上一層樓。

