==續集==
{{main|厲陰宅3：是惡魔逼我的}}
在《厲陰宅2》上映後，[[溫子仁|溫子仁]]受訪時表示，《厲陰宅》還可發展出更多續集。而編劇查德與凱利·海耶斯也表示願意參與續集<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/scene/vpage/conjuring-sequels-james-wan-vera-farmiga-patrick-wilson-1201791090/|title='Conjuring 2' Director James Wan: 'There Could Be Many More Movies'|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|last=McNary|first=Dave|date=2016-06-08|access-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609052628/https://variety.com/2016/scene/vpage/conjuring-sequels-james-wan-vera-farmiga-patrick-wilson-1201791090/|archive-date=2016-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但由於溫子仁還答應了其他的工作邀約，因此有可能沒法繼續執導<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/30/conjuring-3-james-wan|title=James Wan may not have the time to direct The Conjuring 3|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|last=Collis|first=Clark|date=2016-06-08|access-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610084223/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/30/conjuring-3-james-wan|archive-date=2016-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。溫子仁向[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]透露，如果真會有第三集，那他願意參與<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/james-wan-the-conjuring-2-inteview/|title=James Wan on 'The Conjuring 2,' Superheroes, and His Guilty Pleasure Movies|website=[[Collider_(網站)|Collider.com]]|last=Weintraub|first=Steve|date=2016-06-11|access-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612130722/http://collider.com/james-wan-the-conjuring-2-inteview/|archive-date=2016-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>；他也指出，第三集的故事背景最好能發生在1980年代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/15/james-wan-already-has-an-idea-for-the-conjuring-3?abthid=5761207700a747ca67000004|title=James Wan Already Has an Idea For The Conjuring 3|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|first=Chris|last=Tilly|date=2016-06-15|access-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616201720/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/15/james-wan-already-has-an-idea-for-the-conjuring-3?abthid=5761207700a747ca67000004|archive-date=2016-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年6月，宣布新線影業將會推出第三部《厲陰宅》電影，劇本由《厲陰宅2》的編劇之一{{link-en|大衛·萊斯利·強森|David Leslie Johnson}}撰寫<ref name="c3screenwriter">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/the-conjuring-3-movie-new-line-david-leslie-johnson-screenwriter-1202118723/ |title='The Conjuring 3' Is Summoned By New Line; David Leslie Johnson Hired To Script |first=Anita |last=Busch |date=2017-06-26 |website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |access-date=2017-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029212043/http://deadline.com/2017/06/the-conjuring-3-movie-new-line-david-leslie-johnson-screenwriter-1202118723/ |archive-date=2017-10-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年5月，飾演華倫太太的[[薇拉·法蜜嘉|薇拉·法蜜嘉]]在個人社群網站貼出與飾演華倫先生的[[派翠克·威爾森|派翠克·威爾森]]的合照，並聲明第三集即將開拍。

